# Local device reference (example)

Copy this file to **`LOCAL-DEVICES.md`** in the **repository root** (same folder as `README.md`).  
`LOCAL-DEVICES.md` is **gitignored** so UDIDs and personal names are not pushed.

Use the values with `-p:_DeviceName="..."` in `dotnet build` / VS Code task **maui: run iOS physical device**.

Fill in from `mlaunch --listdev` when names or UDIDs change.

| Friendly name | UDID |
|---------------|------|
| My iPhone | `00000000-0000000000000000` |
| Second device | `00000000-0000000000000000` |

Example command:

```bash
cd OWCE
dotnet build OWCE.iOS/OWCE.iOS.csproj -c Debug -f net9.0-ios -r ios-arm64 -t:Run \
  -p:_DeviceName="00000000-0000000000000000"
```
